---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>

<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">

  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
    How Much Money Do You Need for Travel?
  </h1>

  <img
    src="/images/blogs/money.jpg"
    alt="Travel budget"
    class="rounded-3xl w-full h-[420px] object-cover mb-10"
  />

  <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
    Your travel budget depends heavily on your destination, style of travel, and how long you stay.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">1. Budget travellers</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700">Expect €40–€80 per day in cheap countries, more in Australia/NZ.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">2. Mid-range travellers</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700">€80–€150 per day for comfort, activities and private rooms.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">3. Big factor: flights</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700">Long-haul flights often make up 30–50% of your total budget.</p>

</section>

</BaseLayout> 